The Best .vimrc Ever (tm)
===

Requirements:
---

     * Ruby 1.8.7
     * Vim


Installation on Ubuntu:
---

    sudo apt-get install gcc make ruby ruby-dev vim
    mkdir ~/.vim
    git clone git://github.com/nikssardana/vimrc-1 ~/.vim
    ln -s ~/.vim/.vimrc .vimrc
    cd ~/.vim/ruby/command-t
    ruby extconf.rb
    make
